<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Moa - Jira 리포트</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f5f5f7; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; min-height: 100vh; margin: 0; padding: 24px 0; }
        .container { background: white; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); width: 100%; max-width: 440px; }
        h1 { text-align: center; color: #1d1d1f; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
        .modes { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
        .mode-card { text-align: left; border: 2px solid #e5e5ea; border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px; background: #fafafa; cursor: pointer; transition: .15s; }
        .mode-card.active { border-color: #5f0080; background: #f5edfa; }
        .mode-card .mtitle { font-weight: 700; font-size: .95rem; color: #1d1d1f; }
        .mode-card .mdesc { font-size: .75rem; color: #86868b; margin-top: 3px; line-height: 1.3; }
        .form-group { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        label { display: block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; color: #1d1d1f; }
        input, select { width: 100%; padding: 0.8rem; border: 1px solid #d2d2d7; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; box-sizing: border-box; background: white; }
        .help-text { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #86868b; margin-top: 0.25rem; }
        button.submit { width: 100%; padding: 1rem; background-color: #5f0080; color: white; border: none; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
        button.submit:hover { background-color: #6f1090; }
        .token-link { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #0071e3; text-decoration: none; float: right; }
        .greeting { text-align:center; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Moa</h1>

        <div class="modes">
            <div class="mode-card active" id="card-report" onclick="setMode('report')">
                <div class="mtitle">📅 회고 리포트</div>
                <div class="mdesc">연간 내 티켓 회고 (레거시)</div>
            </div>
            <div class="mode-card" id="card-roundup" onclick="setMode('roundup')">
                <div class="mtitle">📊 반기 성과 취합</div>
                <div class="mdesc">기획/기술/KTLO 분류 · 프로덕트앱팀</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        #if(savedEmail):
        <div class="greeting">
            <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; color: #1d1d1f; margin:0;">👋 반가워요, <strong>#(savedEmail)</strong>님!</p>
            <p class="help-text">저장된 계정으로 바로 진행합니다. (토큰 재입력 불필요)</p>
        </div>
        #endif

        <form action="/moa/collect" method="POST" id="mainForm">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="year">연도</label>
                <input type="number" id="year" name="year" value="2026" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group" id="half-group" style="display:none;">
                <label for="half">반기</label>
                <select id="half" name="half">
                    <option value="1">상반기 (1~6월)</option>
                    <option value="2">하반기 (7~12월)</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="platform">플랫폼 (선택)</label>
                <select id="platform" name="platform">
                    <option value="">전체</option>
                    <option value="iOS">iOS</option>
                    <option value="Android">Android</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="email">Jira 이메일</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="example@kurlycorp.com" #if(savedEmail):value="#(savedEmail)"#else:required#endif>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="token">
                    Jira API 토큰
                    <a href="https://id.atlassian.com/manage-profile/security/api-tokens" target="_blank" class="token-link">토큰 발급받기 &rarr;</a>
                </label>
                <input type="password" id="token" name="token" placeholder="#if(savedEmail):저장된 토큰 사용 (비우면 됨)#else:API 토큰을 입력하세요#endif" #if(savedEmail):#else:required#endif>
                <div class="help-text">
                    <p style="margin: 0.2rem 0;">⚠️ 토큰은 생성 직후에만 복사 가능합니다.</p>
                    <p style="margin: 0.2rem 0;">🔒 입력한 토큰은 브라우저 쿠키에 저장됩니다.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="spaceKey">Confluence Space Key (선택)</label>
                <input type="text" id="spaceKey" name="spaceKey" placeholder="예: appr 또는 개인 스페이스 키" #if(savedSpaceKey):value="#(savedSpaceKey)"#endif>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group" id="overrides-group" style="display:none;">
                <label for="epicOverrides">분류 지정 에픽 (선택)</label>
                <textarea id="epicOverrides" name="epicOverrides" rows="3" style="width:100%; padding:0.8rem; border:1px solid #d2d2d7; border-radius:8px; font-size:0.9rem; box-sizing:border-box; font-family:inherit;">기술: KMA-8172, KMA-8594, KMA-8265, KMA-6393, KMA-8266</textarea>
                <div class="help-text">
                    <p style="margin:0.2rem 0;">공통 팀 에픽 지정 — 하위 티켓이 이 에픽으로 묶여 자동 분류(버전 분리 안 함).</p>
                    <p style="margin:0.2rem 0;">형식: <code>카테고리: KMA-키, KMA-키</code> (줄 단위 · 링크도 OK). 카테고리 = 기획/기술/KTLO.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <button type="submit" class="submit" id="submitBtn">📅 회고 리포트 생성</button>
        </form>
    </div>

    <script>
        function setMode(mode) {
            const form = document.getElementById('mainForm');
            const halfGroup = document.getElementById('half-group');
            const overridesGroup = document.getElementById('overrides-group');
            const btn = document.getElementById('submitBtn');
            document.getElementById('card-report').classList.toggle('active', mode === 'report');
            document.getElementById('card-roundup').classList.toggle('active', mode === 'roundup');
            if (mode === 'roundup') {
                form.action = '/moa/roundup';
                halfGroup.style.display = 'block';
                overridesGroup.style.display = 'block';
                btn.innerText = '📊 반기 성과 취합';
            } else {
                form.action = '/moa/collect';
                halfGroup.style.display = 'none';
                overridesGroup.style.display = 'none';
                btn.innerText = '📅 회고 리포트 생성';
            }
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
